description: Try our easy to follow Gluten-Free Raspberry & Custard Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Gluten-Free Raspberry & Custard Cake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 430 g Free From Gluten vanilla cake mix

recipeInstructions.text: Bake for 55 minutes or until cake is golden and a skewer inserted into centre comes out clean. Cool in pan for 10 minutes before transferring to a wire rack to cool completely. Dust cake with icing sugar, then serve with whipped cream and extra raspberries.
